      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-new        not  = spaces
                     go to vis-rig-cor-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Commento                                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-com-rig-000      thru vis-com-rig-999        .
       vis-rig-cor-999.
