      *              * Commento                                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-com-rig-000      thru pmt-com-rig-999        .
       pmt-rig-cor-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione prompt : Commento                         *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-com-rig-000.
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      19                   to   v-car                  .
           move      23                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
