           move      all   "."            to   w-let-arc-pdc-des      .
           go to     let-arc-pdc-999.
       let-arc-pdc-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione work area                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-let-arc-pdc-des      .
       let-arc-pdc-999.
